---
import "../styles/global.css";

import Page from "../layouts/index.astro";
---

<Page
title="Sweet Bakes Chicago - Always Nut Free and Allergy Friendly"
  description="Sweet Bakes Chicago is a nut-free cottage bakery in Chicago. Order custom cakes and allergy-friendly baked goods with confidence. Safe & delicious!"
>
  <main class="bg-color-brand-cream text-color-brand-dark-brown font-body antialiased">

    <section class="relative bg-color-brand-brown pt-16 px-6 text-center text-color-brand-cream">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl mb-4 !text-brand-teal">Splash into Summer!</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light italic">Celebrate with end of the year school parties, birthday parties, and summer Soirées. All with home-made, fresh, and nut free ingredients.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1 flex gap-4 justify-center">
      <img 
        src="/decorated-cookies-cics.avif" 
        alt="Custom CICS Cookies" 
        class="w-1/2 rounded-2xl shadow-sm transform -rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-300"
      />
      <img 
        src="/decorated-cookies-Indiana.avif" 
        alt="Indiana University Cookies" 
        class="w-1/2 rounded-2xl shadow-sm transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-300"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2 space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl text-brand-terracotta">School's Out, Cookies are In!</h2>
        <p class="text-lg/relaxed text-brand-dark-brown">
          Make the final bell even sweeter with our custom decorated cookies. We specialize in 
          <strong>school logos and custom names</strong> to celebrate your graduates in style.
        </p>
        
        <div class="pt-2">
          <a 
            href="/decorated-cookies" 
            class="inline-block bg-brand-terracotta text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-heading font-bold hover:bg-brand-dark-brown transition shadow-sm"
          >
            Order Your Cookies
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-light-cream p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-teal shadow-xs">
        <h3 class="font-heading text-brand-brown mb-2 text-xl">The Sweet Bakes Safety Promise</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-dark-brown">Our kitchen is strictly <strong>nut-safe and allergy-friendly</strong>, so every student can safely enjoy the celebration.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


    <section class="relative py-16 px-6 bg-brand-light-cream overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-10">
    <img src="svgs/strawberry-svgrepo-com.svg" class="absolute top-10 left-10 size-12 rotate-12" alt="" />
    <img src="svgs/lemon-svgrepo-com.svg" class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/4 size-16 -rotate-12" alt="" />
    <img src="svgs/berry-cooking-food-svgrepo-com.svg" class="absolute top-1/4 right-10 size-10 rotate-45" alt="" />
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-10">
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl/tight text-brand-brown">
          Fresh Flavors for Summer Birthdays
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg/relaxed text-brand-dark-brown">
          We believe in <strong class="text-brand-terracotta">sophisticated flavor on the inside</strong> and <strong>pure fun on the outside</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ul class="space-y-5 text-brand-dark-brown">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-xs size-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="svgs/strawberry-svgrepo-com.svg" class="size-6" alt="Strawberry icon" />
          </div>
          <span class="font-medium">Fresh fruit fillings (Strawberry, Lemon, Raspberry)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-xs size-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="svgs/cake-thin-yellow-svgrepo-com.svg" class="size-6" alt="Cake icon" />
          </div>
          <span class="font-medium">Custom themed decorations for kids</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white p-2 rounded-full shadow-xs size-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src="svgs/lemon-svgrepo-com.svg" class="size-6" alt="Lemon icon" />
          </div>
          <span class="font-medium">Light, airy textures perfect for warm Chicago days</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="pt-4">
        <a href="/flavors" class="inline-block bg-brand-terracotta text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-heading font-bold hover:bg-brand-dark-brown transition-colors shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          Explore Flavors
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-brand-teal/20 rounded-3xl -rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
      
      <img 
        src="/cake-hero.avif" 
        alt="Custom Birthday Cake" 
        class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-xl max-w-full h-auto object-cover transform transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
      />
      
      <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center gap-1 border border-brand-teal/10">
        <img src="svgs/strawberry-svgrepo-com.svg" class="size-8" alt="Berry" />
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-grey-green">Summer Fresh</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center rounded-3xl my-12">
  <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl mb-6 text-brand-brown">High-Class Soirées</h2>
  <p class="text-xl/relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 text-brand-dark-brow text-left">
    Hosting a formal garden party or wedding? Elevate the menu with our signature 
    <strong>Sunflower Seed Macarons</strong>—the same classic French texture, now 
    available <strong>without the nut allergy</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
    <img 
      src="/macarons-1-650x433.avif" 
      alt="Elegant Sunflower Seed Macaron Display" 
      class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-sm"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-brand-dark-brown mb-12">
    <div class="p-6 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-brand-brown/5">
      <h4 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-terracotta mb-2">Sunflower Seed Base</h4>
      <p>A rare, inclusive version of the French classic made in-house.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-brand-brown/5">
      <h4 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-terracotta mb-2">Elegant Colors</h4>
      <p>Custom-tinted to match your summer event or wedding palette.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 bg-white/50 rounded-xl border border-brand-brown/5">
      <h4 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-terracotta mb-2">Perfect Favors</h4>
      <p>Beautifully boxed and ribboned for weddings and bridal showers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-4">
    <a 
      href="/macarons" 
      class="inline-block bg-brand-terracotta text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-heading font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-dark-brown transition-colors shadow-sm"
    >
      Order Macarons
    </a>
    <p class="text-sm text-brand-grey-green">
      Available for local Chicago delivery and event setup.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
  </main>
</Page>